Detailed Description

CMSIS Cortex-M3 Device Peripheral Access Layer Header File. This file contains all the peripheral register's definitions, bits definitions and memory mapping for STM32L1xx devices.

Author
MCD Application Team
Version
V2.1.3
Date
04-March-2016 This file contains:
  • Data structures and the address mapping for all peripherals
  • Peripheral's registers declarations and bits definition
  • Macros to access peripherals registers hardware
